==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
From [[wikisource:Preface to the Poems Composed at the Orchid Pavilion|Preface to the Poems Composed at the Orchid Pavilion]], by [[wikipedia:Wang Xizhi|Wang Xizhi]] (王羲之).

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: màolínxiūzhú

===Idiom===
'''[[茂]][[林]][[修竹]]'''

# an exuberant growth of trees and bamboos.

